{"tid":1674303,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"為何香港人反抗？因為警察所做乃是破壞法治精神。","createTime":"2019-10-25T06:43:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T19:37:52.000Z","uid":241364,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d2dd1a6cc6ba2e0a06ab853b195fc6a2ed472d64","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:43:11.000Z","msg":"警察係維護<span style=\"color: red;\">法律</span>的力量，是令法律得到執行的保障。而社會秩序及社會公義，乃是透過<span style=\"color: red;\">法律</span>規定，而<span style=\"color: red;\">假手</span>警察去維護。目前根源問題在於，警察不再僅是維護法律的工具，相反，其遊戲法律，反過來將法律當作其用以控制的工具。一句話概況，香港秩序從「法治」，變成「警治」。或者可能有上面嘅人覺得，冇咩唔好，但要記住，香港立身之本係「法治」。<br />\n<br />\n如果香港不再是由「<span style=\"color: red;\">法治</span>」去<span style=\"color: red;\">規定社會秩序</span>，而是任由「<span style=\"color: red;\">警察</span>」將自己置於<span style=\"color: red;\">法律</span>之上，選擇性執法，選擇性違法，不再是<span style=\"color: red;\">法律</span>的<span style=\"color: red;\">工具</span>，而是法律的操控者，可以為其「需要」而視情況不執法，視情況不符合規定，那麼這些警察就不再是法治的<span style=\"color: red;\">合格工具</span>，亦不應該由納稅人金錢去供養呢啲<span style=\"color: red;\">Dirty police</span>。但，我相信仍有尊重法治嘅警察存在。對你地我想講，警隊係你地嘅信仰，但請謹記，絕不可直接認為警隊=社會穩定嘅守護者，你地嘅職責係保護社會安全冇錯，但你地頭上必須先有一位更大嘅「<span style=\"color: red;\">法律，法治</span>」大佬。如果反過來認為「法律」係警隊施行統治力嘅工具，那麼香港就不再是「<span style=\"color: red;\">法治精神</span>」之地，而是「<span style=\"color: red;\">人治精神，警治精神</span>」之地了。<br />\n<br />\n最後，絕對權力等於絕對腐敗，不受限制的暴力終究會無限膨脹。無論何地皆可適用。<br />\n以及，本人和理非，也絕不贊成各位示威者<span style=\"color: red;\">擲汽油彈</span>、毆打反對者的行為，但對各位貼單張、遊行集會去<span style=\"color: red;\">表達訴求</span>的行為表示理解。<br />\n<br />\n僅以此表達己見"},{"pid":"1cd179d73b03c22d64412745d021da201e9ec6fc","tid":1674303,"uid":7494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:44:11.000Z","msg":"唔好意思, 借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(代POST)【本土X國際戰線】鍾庭耀發起全港大型民調及公投<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1659927\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1659927</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌傳送門﹕<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTRURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=ee8e3eae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a>"},{"pid":"ed0b8eba3612d1ef663012924f58767bffbf8d03","tid":1674303,"uid":172638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:44:27.000Z","msg":"提大家今個星期六日有咩活動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>星期六 10 &middot; 26 醫護抗暴 - 醫療專職集會</strong></span><br />\n- 18:00 遮打花園 [已獲不反對通知書]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>星期日 10 &middot; 27 <br />\n追究警暴 守護民眾記者 守護穆斯林</strong></span><br />\n- 15:00 尖沙咀梳士巴利道公園<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>星期日 10 &middot; 27 自由之鶴追悼會</strong></span><br />\n- 16:00 - 20:00 觀塘海濱公園"},{"pid":"a83f35c5bb920db8d6120a1859e8b9160542c2af","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:45:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6a29f46e28508594aedb932fd7a36111b5ff19c8","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:47:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1c649f40a4d06092b6003674f1b9ae7849e729f0","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:50:36.000Z","msg":"同埋其實各位個個反中共，But，中央其實冇搞香港啊。如果搞香港，會咁細水？其調軍車武警以僅僅係為林鄭撐腰。實際上僅以管控上面輿論為主，這是一貫做法，其實很輕微。至少佢係冇直接插手香港施政。至於傳聞派警察落來，首先都係香港警隊有問題先啊，一味反佢有咩用？問題係警隊。"},{"pid":"fce5e1d09f064b664a5e209b5b182edd8203e675","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:51:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2c50441e877bf69a29e978230a261244e58bbcb1","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:55:44.000Z","msg":"Push，如有反對都請講講你嘅反對意見，理智合邏輯嘅方式。"},{"pid":"560916eda65e7cf2d032c5cc354283bc88da95e1","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:57:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1b3ad23ed1a196b83f28d941a8b7e63f8db792ac","tid":1674303,"uid":318839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:58:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最後，絕對權力等於絕對腐敗，不受限制的暴力終究會無限膨脹。無論何地皆可適用。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以反共好正常<br />\nblocked<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78819c4925bd7c5dbcd44e1897c32829817ada5c","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1b3ad23ed1a196b83f28d941a8b7e63f8db792ac","tid":1674303,"uid":318839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:58:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最後，絕對權力等於絕對腐敗，不受限制的暴力終究會無限膨脹。無論何地皆可適用。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以反共好正常<br />\nblocked<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:00:57.000Z","msg":"依家打人嘅係差佬，開槍嘅係差佬，你去反嘅係什麼？唔去搵兇手，去搵佢個Mind入面你覺得可能令佢打人嘅果股思想？你唔覺得滑稽嗎？非反唔反嘅問題，兇手就係面前，竟然將矛頭指向天邊？"},{"pid":"c3ac2b4849f9f39ec9aaa6d56a591c40db591db5","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:03:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a9004ee860bb9f9051f4b678223cd4c2c1be73e8","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:07:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4a5da63bacbfd22ae8a30f02240f61d013105452","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:09:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"27f9f5a994b79369579b73701922e6b70f4c335e","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:10:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a449d500c614922e4e80cc25f4fc6205d23f749e","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:10:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d85de718d0e64a56b0aa449491c7f78ed24d0361","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c50441e877bf69a29e978230a261244e58bbcb1","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:55:44.000Z","msg":"Push，如有反對都請講講你嘅反對意見，理智合邏輯嘅方式。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:12:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2169182b16fe322b83e56b9653192241c695b738","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:13:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c3f397dbe32c96ac08d92e25f2af06ca862a066b","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:13:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"db5b9387732f6534a6e1530c97e30df2f0287381","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:14:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5ed9eddd8b38a51bbce6e60aadef905264e6239e","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:15:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"573ec4209524a34cb71d91b9037852ebe2e8a4b7","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:17:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e74ac855dd60b3a952edbe7bd9bdd3242f64506e","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:23:11.000Z","msg":"等左咁耐，得一位朋友反對，反對完即刻Blocked埋我呢位與他意見不合者。勇於抗爭嘅人，幾時變得如此封閉？如此畏懼不同嘅聲音？若一個真理係正確嘅，又如何擔心自己會被愚弄分化？至少你應該相信佢呢個信念，並且清楚明白可以講到佢係乜，而不畏懼與其他不同者交流，不會匆忙Blocked人如鴕鳥埋沙。點解唔闡述你嘅意見，去說服看呢個Post嘅人？呢個係一個開放平台，亦冇權力禁止任何人發言。"},{"pid":"310c5a846f333aa2cab361ddef885c72f1c0edd1","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:30:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8b29c3fe7050c831574edbd62c80f77b89a1dedc","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:31:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6e529dc8e2cce56460ed9c4959984527d3633af9","tid":1674303,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c649f40a4d06092b6003674f1b9ae7849e729f0","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:50:36.000Z","msg":"同埋其實各位個個反中共，But，中央其實冇搞香港啊。如果搞香港，會咁細水？其調軍車武警以僅僅係為林鄭撐腰。實際上僅以管控上面輿論為主，這是一貫做法，其實很輕微。至少佢係冇直接插手香港施政。至於傳聞派警察落來，首先都係香港警隊有問題先啊，一味反佢有咩用？問題係警隊。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:35:13.000Z","msg":"唔係中共同777正苦默許同縱容<br />\n黑警會咁過份？<br />\n鄉黑 福建幫 黑警 保皇 中聯辦乃至正苦 中共已經好明顯係一個package，唔洗旨意分割"},{"pid":"7d1bb0b2c3296bb7c22f98a849e47fe98a4aeab5","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:35:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4e5591b7c973b702f25838026478c9a38cf29fa9","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e529dc8e2cce56460ed9c4959984527d3633af9","tid":1674303,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c649f40a4d06092b6003674f1b9ae7849e729f0","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:50:36.000Z","msg":"同埋其實各位個個反中共，But，中央其實冇搞香港啊。如果搞香港，會咁細水？其調軍車武警以僅僅係為林鄭撐腰。實際上僅以管控上面輿論為主，這是一貫做法，其實很輕微。至少佢係冇直接插手香港施政。至於傳聞派警察落來，首先都係香港警隊有問題先啊，一味反佢有咩用？問題係警隊。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:35:13.000Z","msg":"唔係中共同777正苦默許同縱容<br />\n黑警會咁過份？<br />\n鄉黑 福建幫 黑警 保皇 中聯辦乃至正苦 中共已經好明顯係一個package，唔洗旨意分割"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:43:36.000Z","msg":"首先，大家可能對中共冇一個正確認識。佢係有權利「緊急管制」香港，直接派軍車封路，武警捉人。實際上並不需要依賴黑幫、福建幫、鄉黑呢啲對比起來擦鞋都冇份嘅小卒子，其實只係呢啲勢力自己想擦鞋中共，更可能受Dirty議員（何）指使，成為親中議員佢自己嘅政治資本，而非中央授意。<br />\n<br />\n因為中央真正實行影響力，會從其他方面落手先，例如關中銀，經濟方面施加壓力，最後至考慮武警清場。<br />\n<br />\n我同意你講嘅政府縱容，包括警隊亦在縱容。確實令我都感到極度氣憤。但中共決無能力遙距操控警隊指揮官示意手下開槍，示意正苦罔顧法治，即使有壓力施加，首先都係身為香港人嘅特首太廢先會咁企唔硬。"},{"pid":"499c060f0196a1f4a4285274155870d00c544352","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:49:46.000Z","msg":"其實警隊一直有黑，甚至內部有啲嘢一直咁黑，但從來冇俾人爆過出黎。依家只係俾人揭到揚晒，所以先覺得咁得人驚。一位長輩同我交流意見時講嘅。"},{"pid":"c2029c96cade96580435a2b7a1d65916de384b98","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:58:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f0bc03f52e673174f3bb6df4254c7b2a4280d158","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T08:03:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5a20ffb0f0cefcf91fffd9fb2a499c771a947816","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T08:07:08.000Z","msg":"警隊內部自有一套秩序，有時甚至原始而野蠻。<br />\n有一次查飛虎隊Wiki，先知早期佢地training係毫無人道嘅操練，甚至整到有人死。內部秩序嘅森嚴，更加限制警員個人思想，不得不屈服階級命令之下，逐漸習慣成為警隊嘅執行機器。"},{"pid":"c9524dbeec34e7593be56aec1876c32996affb7a","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T08:08:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a8b62427b2b4cd24c41c70871ddcd6d405e2934b","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T08:12:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9a5f7dd1c31857f49032801861dfcbca80f8af87","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T08:14:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"811b4b9efeee4f76a3e37be0ee656ddd55ba257c","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T08:15:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6dda6f029d47a5ecaac0159d7245dcccc2b85d71","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T08:22:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5c77450111fe23647b7dbb621f6889564ebd3f84","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T08:22:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0d1d076f2690690c5f40d310b774a2280ceb4a3b","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T08:26:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c666dba713a3226ab6f73a8a1364e613c847e071","tid":1674303,"uid":241364,"like":0,"dislik